com.konakartadmin.app
Class AdminWishLists

java.lang.Object
  com.konakartadmin.app.AdminWishLists

public class AdminWishLists
extends java.lang.Object

This is the object returned for API calls returning an array of AdminWishLists. It contains an array of AdminWishList objects and the total number of AdminWishLists matching the request, so that they can be paged.

Field Summary
private  int totalNumWishLists
          Total number of wish list items in the database - fewer than this may be returned in the wishLists array!
